\title{matrix multiplication in geometry}
\date{2024-01-17}
\author{jonmsterling}
\taxon{side remark}

\p{Although we do not explore it in [this course](jms-0081), the viewpoint of matrix multiplication as relational composition generalises to a correct explanation of the role of matrices in geometry as presentations of linear maps between vector spaces in terms of an (uncanonical) choice of basis.}